<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id628594a3-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s1952"><num value="1952">§ 1952.</num><heading> Rules and regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Within one hundred and eighty days after <date date="1978-11-08">November 8, 1978</date>, the Secretary shall promulgate such rules and regulations as may be necessary to carry out the provisions of this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id628594a4-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/95/608/tIII/s302">Pub. L. 95–608, title III, § 302</ref>, <date date="1978-11-08">Nov. 8, 1978</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/92/3077">92 Stat. 3077</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
